{"tid":2102068,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中國駐英美大使反北京？ - 李平","createTime":"2020-07-10T08:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T08:14:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c36d1ef333165fe967a76aba8fa1d9a8dd4f1ce3","tid":2102068,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:10:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/TEUJIJJ72NTUPTBXDLIZHN3QTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FTEUJIJJ72NTUPTBXDLIZHN3QTU%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumkxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=6f12cfa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FTEUJIJJ72NTUPTBXDLIZHN3QTU%2F&h=3474b008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/TEUJIJJ72NTUPTBXDLIZHN3QTU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中國駐英美大使反北京？ - 李平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lhpeLFXifWxNV5LyPaJmaKbZyII=/1173x700/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N45EYLPGBGXDBI35YBMUCUW364.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlhpeLFXifWxNV5LyPaJmaKbZyII%3D%2F1173x700%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN45EYLPGBGXDBI35YBMUCUW364.gif&h=ae9b6535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國駐英大使劉曉明早前接受訪問，拒絕排除中國會禁止港人離境，加入英國給予港人的BNO居留權新計劃。且不說中國如何禁止港人離境或進入英國，更惹人關注的是，劉大使的言論明顯與中國外交部發言人趙立堅「中國來去自由」的評論有衝突。更早之前，趙立堅指控新冠病毒源於美軍實驗室，中國駐美大使崔天凱則接受美國媒體訪問指斥有關言論瘋狂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外交部與大使不一致<br />\n<br />\n以官階論，趙立堅是新聞司副司長，即副局級幹部，而中國駐美大使、駐英大使都是副部級高幹。以常理論，在北京的中國外交部發言人更能直接收到中共最高層指示，其言論比駐外官員能更快更好反映中共立場。但發言人的表態接連與駐英大使、駐美大使發生衝突，究竟是外交部有兩個司令部、反映中共最高層權鬥的延伸？還是駐英、駐美大使搞將在外君命有所不受，甚或反北京、鬧獨立？還是有官員低能、屢屢信口開河？<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅是今年2月才出任中國外交部第31任發<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n立堅的臉，也是打在北京的中國外交部的臉。<br />\n<br />\n出人意料的是，中美在武漢肺炎的衝突引發<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n不滿意的人離開香港的輿論倒是一致。<br />\n<br />\n英國正式提出給予持有BNO港人五年居留權後，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n立堅式地對300萬港人的來去自由漠然視之。<br />\n<br />\n可笑的是，趙立堅的漠然固然不諳香港人才<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n外交部發言人與駐英美大使的鬧劇就陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/appledaily.liping\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fappledaily.liping&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumkxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=d42106d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/appledaily.liping</a><br />\n李平"},{"pid":"5051c8d976ba9d1a2c6a6bac5f115e6f8b4065cd","tid":2102068,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"可能有意模糊呢"},{"pid":"a2f05765c2b455f6fe9d6e548b9c6eabf2121ea9","tid":2102068,"uid":18354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"廢話少講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>全</strong></span></span>"}]}